{"type": "article", "id": 8910, "title": "Monkey Business 木塞卡通", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-27T07:16:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235253Cj6TfOrqdW8wmZ1A.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t以色列设计工作室 Reddish Studio 为同样是来自以色列的设计品牌 Monkey Business 带来了一套新的经典的木塞“玩具团”，用木塞的重现了历史上一个个经典的卡通角色。有木头兵“卡尔”，木马“洛基”等等。这些角色都是由酒木塞作为主体，加上小巧的配件辅助组成。Reddish Studio 和 Monkey Business 近几年一直保持合作，推出各式各样木塞人偶。这些玩偶的价格在几美元到十几美元之间不等，<a href=\"http://www.mnkbusiness.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以买到。另外，这是<a href=\"http://www.reddishstudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Reddish Studio 工作室的官方主页</a>，可以看到他们更多的作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235249cMkYqwJyS7zNHG59.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.57037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352498gIxC9vzJmPi1aHe.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352503e21awrpuqgQDZlB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235250eDqCrKOYFTQWlEZk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352512mtKOnaL97SjYxAZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.57777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235251GT9iasV70PjohJYF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.50925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235252tyHW5MmcrDOL2z6q.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235252BXC9vqbVtLSWe3p6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\